<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361644" n="1"/>
  <opener><lb/><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> atque <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Viro <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517"><abbr>P.</abbr> <abbr>An.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
<p><lb/>Parce, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, Vir Amicissime si tamdiu distuli respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sionem ad humanissimas tuas <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517025005501">litteras</rs>, quas una cum
                            <lb/><abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12209025X">Werenfelsii</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">Dissertationibus</rs> jam pridem accepi. Nam
                            <lb/>in mei de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Separatione Fluidor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in Corpore Animali ope<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris</rs> editione atque in <subst><del>f</del><add>M</add></subst>edicina facienda valde occu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>patus continuo fui. Tibi gratias ago maximas, Vir
  <lb/>Doctissime, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">√≤</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d eas <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">Dissertationes</rs> ad me miseris,
                            <lb/>promittoque (statim ac <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3164603">Venetias</rs> redierit) <abbr>Clariss.</abbr>
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Agnato</rs> Tuo restiturum libras 13 pro illis ipsis
  <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationibus</rs>. Fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> meorum <rs type="biblios" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">librorum</rs>
  <lb/>ad vos nond<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pervenisse ipse quoque multum
                              <lb/>admod<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> miror, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim qu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> de ejus ad vos
  <lb/>missione me nuper certior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> fecerit Mulier <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">sa</hi></abbr>
  <lb/>Marchio <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1221330748">Maria Loaysa Butintrochi</rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Medio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lani</rs> est. Statuo itaque ali<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eorund<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
  <lb/><rs type="biblios" key="biblio_M3G2JA79 biblio_43V6EF8W">libror<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3182164">Bergomi</rs> ad <unclear>v</unclear>os transmittere, si
                              <lb/>vobis non displicebit. Rogab<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ƒÅ</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> de responsione ad
  <lb/>obiectionem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccatanam</rs>, rogoque iter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> et Te
                            <lb/>et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> tuum. <subst><del>R</del><add>O</add></subst>bjectio <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccati</rs> talis est. Conces<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>so aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egress<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quantitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tempore quo grave
                              <lb/>motu accelerato describit lineam <formula>IG</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem
                            <lb/>esse <formula>EF \times 2GI</formula>,<del> inquit Riccatus,</del> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccatus</rs> ita ratioci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>natur. Per vim aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> total<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> generante nihil
                            <lb/>aliud intelligit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtonus</rs> nisi vim aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egres<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1361645" n="2"/>
<lb break="no"/><choice><sic>sum</sic><corr>sae</corr></choice> per foramen <formula>EF</formula> sollicitant<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>. Nunc quia posito tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pore constanti vis est semper ut quantitas motus
                              <lb/>sive ut massa ducta in velocitatem, positaque
                              <lb/>etiam velocitate constanti, semper vis erit
  <lb/>ut massa. In casu <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoni</rs>, inquit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccatus</rs>,
                              <lb/>tempus est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale illi, quo gutta aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cadit
                              <lb/>ex altitudine <formula>GI</formula>, velocitas aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> qua ipsa
                              <lb/>aqua exilit <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">√®</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> foramine semper est eadem: igitur
                              <lb/>vis tot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> motum generans <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis est mass<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> illo eod<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tempore egreditur ex
                              <lb/>foramine <formula>EF</formula>. At hujusmodi aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egress<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>quantitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qual<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> esse <formula>EF \times 2GI</formula> concessimus,
                              <lb/>constat ergo vim tot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <add>exilientis</add> mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><del> exilientis</del>
  <lb/>generant<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> esse <formula>= EF \times 2GI</formula> uti dixit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nus</rs>.</p>
  <p><lb/><rs type="letter">Scripsit</rs><note type="internal">Nachgewiesener Brief (in BIBB erfassen)</note> quid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> Tuus ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs><note type="internal">kontrollieren, ob tats√§chlich Nic. II B. gemeint ist, oder vielleicht Dan.</note>,
                            <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccati</rs> demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> esse pur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> putum para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>logism<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, seque postea de hac re fusius scriptur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>,
                              <lb/>verum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> non mihi indicaverit ration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> dete<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gendi paralogism<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, non possum et ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> et
                              <lb/>Te non rogare ut quamprimum mihi osten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>datis ill<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, de quo loquor, paralogismum,
                              <lb/>et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea ostendatis qua ratione tueri possim
                              <lb/>fili aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egredientis per foramen <formula>EF</formula> <subst><del><gap/></del><add>coarcta</add></subst><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem in certa ab ipso foramine distan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1361647" n="3"/>
<lb break="no"/>tia per solam pression<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ƒì</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><sic>framini</sic><corr>foramini</corr></choice>
                            <lb/>incumbentis.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, mihique favere hac in
                                                        <lb/>re <del><gap/> </del>ne dedigneris.</salute> <dateline><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3164603">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1721-07-18">18 Julii 1721.</date></dateline>
                              <pb facs="1361647" n="4"/>
